<html>
<body style="font-family: Arial, sans-serif; font-size: 12px; color: #333;">
  <h2 style="color: #0066cc;">⊘ Exchange Server Maintenance Cancelled</h2>
  
  <table style="border-collapse: collapse; width: 100%; margin: 20px 0;">
    <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold; width: 30%;">Status:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px; color: #0066cc; font-weight: bold;">CANCELLED</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Environment:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ environment_type | upper }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Database:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ target_database }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr>
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Cancellation Time:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ ansible_date_time.iso8601 }}</td>
    </tr>
    <tr style="background-color: #f0f0f0;">
      <td style="padding: 8px; font-weight: bold;">Job ID:</td>
      <td style="padding: 8px;">{{ tower_job_id | default('N/A') }}</td>
    </tr>
  </table>

  <h3 style="color: #0066cc;">Cancellation Details:</h3>
  <div style="background-color: #e6f3ff; padding: 10px; border-left: 4px solid #0066cc; margin: 10px 0;">
    {% if cancellation_reason is defined %}
    <strong>Reason:</strong> {{ cancellation_reason }}
    {% else %}
    <strong>Reason:</strong> User cancelled maintenance workflow
    {% endif %}
  </div>

  <h3 style="color: #228B22;">Status Summary:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>✓ Maintenance workflow was cancelled successfully</li>
    <li>✓ No changes were applied to the Exchange environment</li>
    <li>✓ Server remains in normal operational state</li>
    <li>✓ All services are running normally</li>
    <li>✓ No cleanup actions required</li>
  </ul>

  <div style="background-color: #f0f0f0; padding: 15px; margin: 20px 0; border-left: 4px solid #228B22;">
    <strong>Important:</strong> The Exchange server was not affected by this cancelled maintenance workflow. All systems are operating normally and no manual intervention is required.
  </div>

  <h3 style="color: #0066cc;">Next Steps:</h3>
  <ul>
    <li>The maintenance window has been released</li>
    <li>The scheduled maintenance may be rescheduled for a later date</li>
    <li>No urgent action is required at this time</li>
    <li>Contact the team to reschedule if necessary</li>
  </ul>

  <hr style="margin: 20px 0; border: none; border-top: 1px solid #ccc;">
  <p style="font-size: 11px; color: #666;">
    This is an automated notification from the STAMP Exchange Maintenance Automation system.<br>
    For support or to reschedule maintenance, contact: {{ notifications.default_contacts | join(', ') }}
  </p>
</body>
</html>
